<title>Isa, rızamyn РӘЖ248</title>
<lyrics>[C1]
.              G C
   Isa, rızamyn,
.                            D G
   Tildesem Senimen árqashan,
.               G                    C D G
   Isa, rızamyn, meniń Qamqorshymsyń.

[V1]
.         G             C
 Qýansam da, jylasam da,
.                   D
 Saǵan kelip aıtamyn
.      G                             C D G
 Bar syrymdy aqtaramyn Seniń aldyńda.

[V2]
 Baspanamsyń, panalaımyn
 Qanatyńnyń astyna.
 Qaýipsizbin men aıaly alaqanyńda.

[V3]
 Júregimdi bilesiń Sen,
 Senimen máńgi qalamyn,
 O, Táńir, ómirimdi Saǵan tapsyramyn.</lyrics>
<key>G</key>
